Data Source: City of Bellingham / Public Works / Operations / Plants / Laboratory
Stream discharge data provided by the City of Bellingham that is dated prior to 10/1/2021 have been subjected to review and are substantially complete.
The City of Bellingham may revise reviewed data pursuant to further analysis and review as needed.
Stream discharge data provided by the City of Bellingham that is dated from 10/1/2021 or later are preliminary and have not received final approval.
Inaccuracies in the data may be present because of instrument malfunctions or physical changes at the measurement site.
Subsequent review may result in significant revisions to the data.
